# Ignore all project-local skill dirs by default; explicitly allow the
# ACT project skills that are tracked in this repo. New/personal skills
# dropped into .claude/skills/ will be silently ignored. To commit a new
# project skill, add `!.claude/skills/<name>/` below and force-add once.
